repository-code: "https://github.com/danielkremen818/ultracost"
url: "https://github.com/danielkremen818/ultracost#readme"
abstract: >-
  Per-stage model routing for Claude Code ultracode dynamic workflows. ultracost
  keeps a single fan-out from silently running every subagent on Opus by injecting
  an explicit per-stage routing policy each session, statically guarding agent()
  stages that would inherit the session model, and gating every dynamic-workflow
  launch with a cost estimate.
keywords:
  - claude-code
  - ultracode
  - dynamic-workflows
  - subagents
  - model-routing
  - cost-optimization
